  "description": "### **A Slice of Paradise in the Heart of Marbella's Golden Mile**\n\n**Location, Location, Location!**\n\nWelcome to your dream holiday home—an architectural gem nestled in the very heart of Marbella’s Golden Mile, arguably the most coveted stretch of real estate on the Costa del Sol. Just 150 metres from the golden sands and palm-lined promenade, this villa offers the ultimate blend of tranquility and proximity—steps away from iconic landmarks like Puente Romano and the Marbella Club, as well as the city’s finest restaurants, boutiques, and beach clubs.\n\n---\n\n### **A Contemporary Oasis with Everything You Could Wish For**\n\nThis newly built, contemporary villa is designed for effortless elegance and indulgent comfort. Tucked just behind the beachfront promenade, you’ll enjoy a serene and private setting while being only moments away from the vibrant pulse of Marbella life.\n\nStep inside and discover five spacious double bedrooms, all ensuite, offering stylish privacy for every guest. The Master suite even boasts a stunning natural stone bathtub, perfect for unwinding after a day in the sun.\n\nThe ground floor flows seamlessly with open-plan living, featuring a sophisticated lounge with a designer fireplace, a sleek dining area, and a fully equipped kitchen complete with breakfast bar and views to the lush garden and sparkling pool. Floor-to-ceiling sliding doors invite the outdoors in, filling the space with natural light and Mediterranean breeze.\n\n---\n\n### **Soak Up the Marbella Lifestyle**\n\nOutside, the private garden surrounds a sun-drenched pool, where loungers and a shaded terrace lounge offer space for both relaxation and entertaining. Whether you’re sipping a morning coffee, enjoying a family barbecue, or reclining with a glass of rosé, this villa was built for slow, joyful living.\n\nUpstairs, a panoramic rooftop terrace steals the show—with an outdoor kitchen, a jacuzzi, and a chill-out lounge where sunset cocktails become unforgettable memories.\n\nFor movie nights or a cool escape from the midday sun, the cinema room downstairs is equipped with a huge screen and sumptuous reclining leather chairs—your own private screening haven.\n\n---\n\n### **Walk Everywhere. Experience Everything.**\n\nOne of the few places in Marbella where a car truly isn’t needed, this villa offers the luxury of **freedom**. Wander along the promenade to the glamour of Puerto Banús, or stroll into the charm of Marbella’s Old Town. Indulge in the spontaneous, relaxed rhythm of coastal life—with everything you need just moments from your doorstep.\n\n---\n\n**Please note:** This property is suited for families and mature couples. We do not accept groups under 30, nor hen or stag parties. If you fall outside of this category but are still interested, feel free to reach out with some details—we’re happy to consider each request individually.\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you to a truly unforgettable Marbella experience.",
